item.title: CVE-2021-20430|2024-08-03T17:37:24.186Z -- ibm -- i2%20analyze
item.description: IBM i2 Analyst's Notebook Premium (IBM i2 Analyze 4.3.0, 4.3.1, and 4.3.2) could allow a remote attacker to obtain sensitive information when a detailed technical error message is returned in the browser. This information could be used in further attacks against the system. IBM X-Force ID: 196341.
